@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Trip to Jaipur";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1, h2 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewBag.Title</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Jaipur, the Pink City of India!</p>
        <h2>Things to Do</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Visit the majestic <strong>Amer Fort</strong>.</li>
            <li>Explore the intricate designs of <strong>Hawa Mahal</strong>.</li>
            <li>Marvel at the grandeur of <strong>City Palace</strong>.</li>
            <li>Shop for handicrafts and textiles at <strong>Johari Bazaar</strong>.</li>
            <li>Take a stroll in the lush gardens of <strong>Sisodia Rani Ka Bagh</strong>.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Places to Eat</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Enjoy traditional Rajasthani cuisine at <strong>Chokhi Dhani</strong>.</li>
            <li>Savor delicious street food at <strong>MI Road</strong>.</li>
            <li>Indulge in fine dining at <strong>Suvarna Mahal</strong>.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Transportation</h2>
        <p>Jaipur is well-connected by air, rail, and road. The city also has a reliable public transportation system including buses and auto-rickshaws.</p>
        <h2>Accommodation</h2>
        <p>There are plenty of accommodation options in Jaipur ranging from luxury hotels to budget guesthouses. Some popular choices include <strong>Rambagh Palace</strong>, <strong>Jaipur Marriott Hotel</strong>, and <strong>Hostel Bagpack Village</strong>.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

